34
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:47,840
Maren Smith and Dan Vanilovic probably don't need any introduction in this room,

35
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:52,020
but they bring a lot of expertise to this table.

36
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:56,680
