59
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:38,000
And so a lot has been done.

60
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:39,740
There's been a big rush.

61
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:43,140
The tariff threat has caused this government to move quickly.

62
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:45,100
