67
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:11,960
And it's great to have Michelle speak to that earlier.

68
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:18,340
So we're looking at proposed legislation from this government that has some pretty significant changes

69
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:24,700
about how energy projects are assessed, including the major North Coast transmission line.

70
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:30,340
