71
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:34,440
But we also need to make sure that we don't rush to get this wrong.

72
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,520
So we need to get this right.

73
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:42,040
And I know we all, and I share the frustration, the government moves can move quite slowly.

74
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:47,360
But to take some of these bills, Bill 7 is the most notable one that you'll have heard of.

75
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:53,960
Bills 14 and 15 are streamlining but concentrating a huge amount of power in the cabinet

76
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:57,420
