93
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:31,680
And this really, clean energy should be non-partisan.

94
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:34,160
This is about how we, this is the way forward.

95
00:07:34,260 --> 00:07:37,600
We all know this is the way forward, and we have to, we have some catching up to do.

96
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:40,980
But it should not be driven by partisanship.

